  <summary date="2021-05-17T14:11:31Z" status="Introduced in House">Paris Agreement Constitutional Treaty Act

This bill prohibits taking any action to carry out the goals of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change&#8212;commonly known as the Paris Agreement&#8212;unless the Senate first ratifies the agreement. Further, the bill prohibits the use of any funds to advance the agreement.</summary>
